fields.calculatedFormula:
IF( RecordType.DeveloperName = "Standard_Question" &&  ISBLANK(Question_Group__c),
"Standard Question: " & Custom_Label__c,
IF( RecordType.DeveloperName = "Standard_Question" &&  NOT(ISBLANK(Question_Group__c)),
"Standard Question: " & Custom_Label__c & " (Group=" & Question_Group__c & ")",
IF( RecordType.DeveloperName = "Custom_Question" &&  ISBLANK(Question_Group__c),
"Custom Question: " & Question__c & " - Question Type: " & TEXT( Question_Type__c ),
"Custom Question: " & Question__c & " - Question Type: " & TEXT( Question_Type__c ) & " (Group=" & Question_Group__c & ")")))
